{"tid":879115,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對抗中國霸權！台、港、蒙、維、藏人等成立自由印太聯盟","createTime":"2018-10-27T16:17:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-27T16:37:21.000Z","uid":184679,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6f95ffd4bc5bff6210f3727f051673e49acea79a","tid":879115,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T16:17:06.000Z","msg":"流亡藏人、南蒙古、維吾爾、香港以及台灣代表，昨天在日本宣佈成立「自由印太聯盟」，對抗中國殖民霸權。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/fn2N9IYhBuWw0Shqhw8ytA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTM2MA--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/lUvRu3VRJGQjPf_3z6mFmQ--~B/aD01NzY7dz0xMDI0O3NtPTE7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/ftvn.com.tw/9d8ed7bfa581b11727b145ed015f64ec\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Ffn2N9IYhBuWw0Shqhw8ytA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTM2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FlUvRu3VRJGQjPf_3z6mFmQ--~B%2FaD01NzY7dz0xMDI0O3NtPTE7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fftvn.com.tw%2F9d8ed7bfa581b11727b145ed015f64ec&h=e7643502&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n維吾爾代表熱比婭、和南蒙古代表席海明等人，在會中分別發言，介紹各自的理念與訴求，以及對中共殖民的抗議。<br />\n<br />\n自由印太聯盟的成立，靈感來自於美國、日本與印度等國提出「印太戰略」，反制中共霸權擴張。<br />\n<br />\n聯盟成員認為，為了維護印太地區的自由、和平與人權，不能只有政府間的軍事與安全合作，還需要印太各民族、各地區的民間力量的串聯與合作才行。自由印太聯盟的祕書處設在東京。<br />\n<br />\n（民視新聞／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ftv.com.tw/news/detail/2018A27W0017\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ftv.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F2018A27W0017&d=OwLvdmaINEXasGCo93XTIrr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=fc57abb0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ftv.com.tw/news/detail/2018A27W0017</a>"},{"pid":"7c8d55b09dc1826d099c131329f1346069976582","tid":879115,"uid":45914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T16:18:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c41e329aea6aea28c9c8e8379b1182b2e175329a","tid":879115,"uid":198583,"like":0,"disli